    // For example:
    let probabilities = {
        C: 0.7,
        CL: 0.2,
        D: 0.1
    };
    // Return the probability for CL outcome
    return probabilities.CL;
}
``` 

With this change, when you call the function with the input values, it will return the probability for the "CL" outcome.
